          "name": "Upon a small Isle",
          "description": "Plants poke their tops above the water in the murky shallows where the isle ends and Breceliande begins. A rotting makeshift dock sinks slowly into the water, unkept and unused for ages. Paths lead off in several directions upon the isle, twisting and turning about the numerous willows and plants growing from the fertile island soil. You have lost 880 experience.",
