        "3629": {
          "vnum": 3629,
          "name": "Lush Foliage",
          "description": "Dense, vibrant vegetation surrounds this part of the path, with towering trees, ferns, and vines creating a verdant canopy above. The air is heavy with humidity and the scent of damp earth, while the distant sounds of wildlife echo through the foliage. The lush growth creates an almost otherworldly atmosphere, enveloping travelers in a cocoon of greenery as they traverse the winding trail.",
